name: Ellie
description:
is a character in the video games The Last of Us by Naughty Dog.
Ellie is described as "mature beyond her years" as a result of the circumstances of her environment.
Having lost many people in her life, she suffers from severe monophobia and survivor's guilt 
this results in her becoming a very hardened person.
She displays great physical resilience, emotional strength, and complete fearlessness.

#064 TLOU Pack
